Package org.jboss.elemento.intl

Interface Duration

@JsType(isNative=true, namespace="<global>") public interface Duration
Mapping for Temporal.Duration.

In addition to the actual mappings, this class implements the builder pattern to create the options easily and in a type-safe manner.

See Also:
  • https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Temporal/Duration
